h":"/modern-documentation/api","tagsPath":"/modern-documentation/api/tags","isLast":true,"routePriority":-1,"sidebarFilePath":"/Users/zhangweixin/Documents/modern-documentation/api/sidebar.ts","contentPath":"/Users/zhangweixin/Documents/modern-documentation/api","docs":[{"id":"ai-core-api","title":"AI Core API","description":"Mock OpenAPI spec for AI Core Docs demo.","source":"@site/api/ai-core-api.info.mdx","sourceDirName":".","slug":"/ai-core-api","permalink":"/modern-documentation/api/ai-core-api","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"editUrl":null,"tags":[],"version":"current","sidebarPosition":0,"frontMatter":{"id":"ai-core-api","title":"AI Core API","description":"Mock OpenAPI spec for AI Core Docs demo.","sidebar_label":"Introduction","sidebar_position":0,"hide_title":true,"custom_edit_url":null},"sidebar":"apisidebar","previous":{"title":"API Reference","permalink":"/modern-documentation/api/"},"next":{"title":"Create a chat completion","permalink":"/modern-documentation/api/create-chat-completion"}},{"id":"create-chat-completion","title":"Create a chat completion","description":"Create a chat completion","source":"@site/api/create-chat-completion.api.mdx","sourceDirName":".","slug":"/create-chat-completion","permalink":"/modern-documentation/api/create-chat-completion","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"editUrl":null,"tags":[],"version":"current","frontMatter":{"id":"create-chat-completion","title":"Create a chat completion","description":"Create a chat completion","sidebar_label":"Create a chat completion","hide_title":true,"hide_table_of_contents":true,"api":"","sidebar_class_name":"post api-method","info_path":"api/ai-core-api","custom_edit_url":null},"sidebar":"apisidebar","previous":{"title":"Introduction","permalink":"/modern-documentation/api/ai-core-api"}},{"id":"index","title":"API Reference","description":"AI Core API reference generated from OpenAPI.","source":"@site/api/index.mdx","sourceDirName":".","slug":"/","permalink":"/modern-documentation/api/","draft":false,"unlisted":false,"tags":[],"version":"current","frontMatter":{"title":"API Reference","slug":"/","description":"AI Core API reference generated from OpenAPI."},"sidebar":"apisidebar","next":{"title":"Introduction","permalink":"/modern-documentation/api/ai-core-api"}}],"drafts":[],"sidebars":{"apisidebar":[{"type":"doc","id":"index"},{"type":"doc","id":"ai-core-api"},{"type":"category","label":"Chat","items":[{"type":"doc","id":"create-chat-completion","label":"Create a chat completion","className":"api-method post","translatable":true}],"collapsed":true,"collapsible":true}]}}]}},"docusaurus-plugin-content-blog":{"default":{"blogSidebarTitle":"Recent posts","blogPosts":[{"id":"gpt-4o-release-notes","metadata":{"permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/gpt-4o-release-notes","editUrl":"https://github.com/zweixin798/modern-documentation/tree/main/blog/2026-03-18-gpt-4o-changelog.md","source":"@site/blog/2026-03-18-gpt-4o-changelog.md","title":"GPT-4o 模型上线更新日志","description":"我们已在 AI Core 平台正式上线 GPT-4o 系列模型，并同步增强了多模态与函数调用体验。","date":"2026-03-18T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Changelog","permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/tags/changelog","description":"Release notes and product updates"}],"readingTime":1,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Zhang Weixin","title":"Maintainer","url":"https://github.com/zweixin798","page":{"permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/authors/zweixin-798"},"socials":{"github":"https://github.com/zweixin798"},"imageURL":"https://github.com/zweixin798.png","key":"zweixin798"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"gpt-4o-release-notes","title":"GPT-4o 模型上线更新日志","authors":["zweixin798"],"tags":["changelog"]},"unlisted":false,"nextItem":{"title":"Welcome","permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/welcome"}},"content":"我们已在 **AI Core** 平台正式上线 **GPT-4o** 系列模型，并同步增强了多模态与函数调用体验。\n\n<!-- truncate -->\n\n## 新增能力\n\n- **更强的对话质量**：在长上下文下的指令遵循与表达更稳定。\n- **更顺滑的工具调用**：函数调用（tool calls）输出更结构化，更适合与工作流编排结合。\n- **更友好的工程集成**：API 兼容 `POST /v1/chat/completions`，更易迁移与替换。\n\n## 兼容性说明\n\n- **API 路径**：保持 `/v1/chat/completions`。\n- **参数**：`messages`、`temperature`、`max_tokens` 等保持一致；新增/增强 `tools` 与 `tool_choice` 的使用体验。\n- **响应**：在触发工具调用时，`finish_reason` 可能为 `tool_calls`，并返回 `tool_calls` 结构。\n\n## 建议升级方式\n\n1. 先在灰度环境切换 `model` 为 `gpt-4o` 或 `gpt-4o-mini`。\n2. 对关键任务启用 **结构化输出**（JSON Schema）并添加校验。\n3. 若你使用 RAG，请同时监控“检索命中率”和“引用一致性”，避免高召回但低相关导致误答。\n\n## 下一步\n\n- 我们会在后续版本补齐更多 SDK 示例与最佳实践（Prompt 规范、工具调用模式、RAG 评测方法）。"},{"id":"welcome","metadata":{"permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/welcome","editUrl":"https://github.com/zweixin798/modern-documentation/tree/main/blog/2021-08-26-welcome/index.md","source":"@site/blog/2021-08-26-welcome/index.md","title":"Welcome","description":"Docusaurus blogging features are powered by the blog plugin.","date":"2021-08-26T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Facebook","permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/tags/facebook","description":"Facebook tag description"},{"inline":false,"label":"Hello","permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/tags/hello","description":"Hello tag description"},{"inline":false,"label":"Docusaurus","permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/tags/docusaurus","description":"Docusaurus tag description"}],"readingTime":0.56,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Sébastien Lorber","title":"Docusaurus maintainer","url":"https://sebastienlorber.com","page":{"permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/authors/all-sebastien-lorber-articles"},"socials":{"x":"https://x.com/sebastienlorber","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/sebastienlorber/","github":"https://github.com/slorber","newsletter":"https://thisweekinreact.com"},"imageURL":"https://github.com/slorber.png","key":"slorber"},{"name":"Yangshun Tay","title":"Ex-Meta Staff Engineer, Co-founder GreatFrontEnd","url":"https://linkedin.com/in/yangshun","page":{"permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/authors/yangshun"},"socials":{"x":"https://x.com/yangshunz","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/yangshun/","github":"https://github.com/yangshun","newsletter":"https://www.greatfrontend.com"},"imageURL":"https://github.com/yangshun.png","key":"yangshun"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"welcome","title":"Welcome","authors":["slorber","yangshun"],"tags":["facebook","hello","docusaurus"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"GPT-4o 模型上线更新日志","permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/gpt-4o-release-notes"},"nextItem":{"title":"MDX Blog Post","permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/mdx-blog-post"}},"content":"[Docusaurus blogging features](https://docusaurus.io/docs/blog) are powered by the [blog plugin](https://docusaurus.io/docs/api/plugins/@docusaurus/plugin-content-blog).\n\nHere are a few tips you might find useful.\n\n<!-- truncate -->\n\nSimply add Markdown files (or folders) to the `blog` directory.\n\nRegular blog authors can be added to `authors.yml`.\n\nThe blog post date can be extracted from filenames, such as:\n\n- `2019-05-30-welcome.md`\n- `2019-05-30-welcome/index.md`\n\nA blog post folder can be convenient to co-locate blog post images:\n\n![Docusaurus Plushie](./docusaurus-plushie-banner.jpeg)\n\nThe blog supports tags as well!\n\n**And if you don't want a blog**: just delete this directory, and use `blog: false` in your Docusaurus config."},{"id":"mdx-blog-post","metadata":{"permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/mdx-blog-post","editUrl":"https://github.com/zweixin798/modern-documentation/tree/main/blog/2021-08-01-mdx-blog-post.mdx","source":"@site/blog/2021-08-01-mdx-blog-post.mdx","title":"MDX Blog Post","description":"Blog posts support Docusaurus Markdown features, such as MDX.","date":"2021-08-01T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Docusaurus","permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/tags/docusaurus","description":"Docusaurus tag description"}],"readingTime":0.27,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Sébastien Lorber","title":"Docusaurus maintainer","url":"https://sebastienlorber.com","page":{"permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/authors/all-sebastien-lorber-articles"},"socials":{"x":"https://x.com/sebastienlorber","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/sebastienlorber/","github":"https://github.com/slorber","newsletter":"https://thisweekinreact.com"},"imageURL":"https://github.com/slorber.png","key":"slorber"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"mdx-blog-post","title":"MDX Blog Post","authors":["slorber"],"tags":["docusaurus"]},"unlisted":false,"prevItem":{"title":"Welcome","permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/welcome"},"nextItem":{"title":"Long Blog Post","permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/long-blog-post"}},"content":"Blog posts support [Docusaurus Markdown features](https://docusaurus.io/docs/markdown-features), such as [MDX](https://mdxjs.com/).\n\n:::tip\n\nUse the power of React to create interactive blog posts.\n\n:::\n\n{/* truncate */}\n\nFor example, use JSX to create an interactive button:\n\n```js\n<button onClick={() => alert('button clicked!')}>Click me!</button>\n```\n\n<button onClick={() => alert('button clicked!')}>Click me!</button>"},{"id":"long-blog-post","metadata":{"permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/long-blog-post","editUrl":"https://github.com/zweixin798/modern-documentation/tree/main/blog/2019-05-29-long-blog-post.md","source":"@site/blog/2019-05-29-long-blog-post.md","title":"Long Blog Post","description":"This is the summary of a very long blog post,","date":"2019-05-29T00:00:00.000Z","tags":[{"inline":false,"label":"Hello","permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/tags/hello","description":"Hello tag description"},{"inline":false,"label":"Docusaurus","permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/tags/docusaurus","description":"Docusaurus tag description"}],"readingTime":2.04,"hasTruncateMarker":true,"authors":[{"name":"Yangshun Tay","title":"Ex-Meta Staff Engineer, Co-founder GreatFrontEnd","url":"https://linkedin.com/in/yangshun","page":{"permalink":"/modern-documentation/blog/authors/yangshun"},"socials":{"x":"https://x.com/yangshunz","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/yangs